The maximum number of URLs a user who does not meet the "<b>Auto-Moderation: Minimum Post Count</b>" can post in a new thread or reply. <br /><br />If the number of URLs posted is more than the defined value here, the post will be automatically placed under Moderation. For example:<br /><br /><i> * If the setting is 0, the user can't post any URLs. <br/ > * If the setting is 1, the user can post up to 1 URL before being moderated.</i><br /><br />Any posts found to exceed the defined limit will be sent to moderation if this user has less than the minimum post count.